Recoding Values with case_when() (Old Way)
Problem: Using case_when() with multiple == checks for simple value mapping

penguins |&gt;
  slice(1:4) |&gt;
  select(species, island, body_mass_g) |&gt;
  mutate(
    island_location = case_when(
      island == "Biscoe" ~ "Southwest",
      island == "Dream" ~ "Northwest",
      island == "Torgersen" ~ "Northwest",
      .default = island
    )
  )

# A tibble: 4 × 4
  species island    body_mass_g island_location
  &lt;fct&gt;   &lt;fct&gt;           &lt;int&gt; &lt;chr&gt;          
1 Adelie  Torgersen        3750 Northwest      
2 Adelie  Torgersen        3800 Northwest      
3 Adelie  Torgersen        3250 Northwest      
4 Adelie  Torgersen          NA Northwest      


Problem with unmatched values:

# Unmatched values become NA
penguins |&gt;
  slice(1:5) |&gt;
  select(species, island, body_mass_g) |&gt;
  mutate(
    size = case_when(
      body_mass_g &gt; 4500 ~ "Large",
      body_mass_g &lt; 3500 ~ "Small"
      # Missing .default, so 3500-4500 becomes NA
    )
  )

# A tibble: 5 × 4
  species island    body_mass_g size 
  &lt;fct&gt;   &lt;fct&gt;           &lt;int&gt; &lt;chr&gt;
1 Adelie  Torgersen        3750 &lt;NA&gt; 
2 Adelie  Torgersen        3800 &lt;NA&gt; 
3 Adelie  Torgersen        3250 Small
4 Adelie  Torgersen          NA &lt;NA&gt; 
5 Adelie  Torgersen        3450 Small

Replacing Values with case_when() (Old Way)
Problem: Using case_when() with .default for simple replacements

# Cap body_mass_g at 5000g
penguins |&gt;
  slice(1:4) |&gt;
  select(species, island, body_mass_g) |&gt;
  mutate(
    body_mass_g_capped = case_when(
      body_mass_g &gt; 5000 ~ 5000,
      .default = body_mass_g  # Must specify .default even though it's the same column
    )
  )

# A tibble: 4 × 4
  species island    body_mass_g body_mass_g_capped
  &lt;fct&gt;   &lt;fct&gt;           &lt;int&gt;              &lt;dbl&gt;
1 Adelie  Torgersen        3750               3750
2 Adelie  Torgersen        3800               3800
3 Adelie  Torgersen        3250               3250
4 Adelie  Torgersen          NA                 NA


Even for single replacements:

# Replace just Northwest with a longer name
penguins |&gt;
  slice(1:4) |&gt;
  select(species, island, body_mass_g) |&gt;
  mutate(
    island_location = case_when(
      island == "Biscoe" ~ "Southwest",
      island == "Dream" ~ "Northwest",
      island == "Torgersen" ~ "Northwest"
    )
  ) |&gt;
  mutate(
    island_location = case_when(
      island_location == "Northwest" ~ "Northern Palmer Archipelago",
      .default = island_location  # Boilerplate!
    )
  )

# A tibble: 4 × 4
  species island    body_mass_g island_location            
  &lt;fct&gt;   &lt;fct&gt;           &lt;int&gt; &lt;chr&gt;                      
1 Adelie  Torgersen        3750 Northern Palmer Archipelago
2 Adelie  Torgersen        3800 Northern Palmer Archipelago
3 Adelie  Torgersen        3250 Northern Palmer Archipelago
4 Adelie  Torgersen          NA Northern Palmer Archipelago
